        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="projects" id="projects">
        <div class="card-project" id="card-project-1">
          <div class="title">
            <h2>Around</h2>
            <div class="selector">
              <div>I want</div>
              <span
                class="material-symbols-outlined disabled"
                data-name="around"
                data-status="1">toggle_on</span
